            <title><![CDATA[Trump hails Iran deal as G7 summit begins in Europe]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/trump-hails-iran-deal-as-g7-summit-begins-in-europe</link>
            <description><![CDATA[The United States and Iran appear closer to extending their shaky ceasefire after both sides electronically signed a memorandum that aims to end the war. But key questions remain ahead of its official signing later this week. The deal was center stage in France on Monday, where President Trump joined other world leaders for the G7 summit. Liz Landers reports. ]]></description>
